    "rationale": "The FEA ensemble demonstrates satisfactory agreement with bench data across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96, difference < 10%). Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed; eleven meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The single below-required factor (Test conditions, achieved 1 vs. required 2) is accepted on the basis of regulatory precedent for ASTM F1717 single-condition submissions. The package is approved for regulatory submission supporting the 510(k) for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw system.",
